Blurb::
Selects the weight function for the MLS model

Description::

The weight function decays as a function of distance from the training
data.  Specify one of:

\li 1 (default):  exponential decay in weight function; once differentiable MLS model    

\li 2: twice differentiable MLS model

\li 3: three times differentiable MLS model

